      • getDhcp

        public String getDhcp()
        Returns:
        The IP address offered by DHCP to network interface 0. If unset, no address is offered. Set to 'auto' to allocate a temporary IP at boot.

      • getModel

        public Model getModel()
        Returns:

      • getVlan

      • getMac

        public String getMac()
        Returns:
